content.description: This mapping loads data from the Redshift underwriting_dashboard_question_reply_stg table to the Redshift uw_dashboard_question_reply_details table
content.name: cdi_map_uw_silver_uw_dashboard_question_reply_details_ld

object.customQuery:
SELECT DISTINCT 
prkr.policy_system_id,
prkr.policy_number,
prkr.policy_module_number,
prkr.policy_key,
q.source_system_system_id AS question_reply_system_id,
q.underwriting_question_and_answer_row_source_system_key AS src_id,
q.underwriting_question_and_answer_type AS question_reply_record_type,
q.underwriting_question_code AS uw_question,
q.underwriting_answer AS uw_answer,
q.parent_or_child_indicator,
q.parent_question_code_of_child_question,
q.question_and_answer_hierarchy,
q.display_question_and_answer_indicator,
udqrd.uw_dashboard_question_reply_details_row_id as  tgt_row_id,
udqrd.uw_dashboard_question_reply_details_md5_hash_value as tgt_md5_hash_key
FROM  silver.underwriting_questions_and_answers q
LEFT JOIN dbo.policy_risk_key_reference prkr
ON q.source_system_system_id = prkr.policy_system_id
AND q.underwriting_question_and_answer_type = prkr.policy_cmm_container 
LEFT JOIN dbo.uw_dashboard_question_reply_details udqrd 
on q.underwriting_question_and_answer_row_source_system_key = udqrd.question_reply_id
and q.source_system_system_id =  udqrd.question_reply_system_id
and q.underwriting_question_and_answer_type = udqrd.question_reply_record_type
and udqrd.uw_dashboard_question_reply_details_row_effective_end_datetime = '9999-12-31'
WHERE prkr.policy_risk_key_reference_row_effective_end_date = '9999-12-31'
and q.underwriting_question_and_answer_row_effective_end_datetime = '9999-12-31'
and q.underwriting_question_and_answer_row_effective_start_datetime >= $LASTRUNTIME

attributes.name: Download S3 Files In Multiple Parts

fields.name: src_md5_hash_value
fields.expression:
MD5('policy_system_id' || to_char(policy_system_id) || 
'policy_number' || policy_number || 
'policy_module_number' || policy_module_number || 
'policy_key' || policy_key || 
'question_reply_system_id' || question_reply_system_id ||
'src_id' || src_id ||
'question_reply_record_type' || question_reply_record_type || 
'uw_question' || uw_question || 
'uw_answer' || uw_answer ||
'parent_or_child_indicator' || parent_or_child_indicator || 
'parent_question_code_of_child_question' || parent_question_code_of_child_question ||
'question_and_answer_hierarchy' || to_char(question_and_answer_hierarchy) ||
'display_question_and_answer_indicator' || display_question_and_answer_indicator)
